
usage: lpkg [option...] mode [mode_option...] [mode_arguement...]
       lpkg install package [package...]
       lpkg update [package...]
       lpkg remove [package...]
       lpkg autoremove
       lpkg info package
       lpkg list
       lpkg dbquery sql_stmt

Leaf Package Manager, a binary package manager for unix-like systems.

options:
  -f dbfile     use alternate database file
  -t            terse, log only necessary information
  -v            verbose, log extra information

modes:
  install       install a package by name or path
  update        update listed packages or if none provided all packages
  remove        remove listed packages
  autoremove    remove orphaned packages
  info          query information about a package
  list          query a list of installed packages
  dbquery       direct manipulation of the database
  help          display this page
  version       display version and copyright page

